### CollectAsmSymbols() {#afeaa3f8d791f06d24dbe1ed910c27a9a}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>void ModuleSymbolTable::CollectAsmSymbols (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module">Module</a> &amp; M, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/function-ref">function&#95;ref</a>&lt; void(<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a>, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/basicsymbolref/#a9004a106627deafd45a7c95ee497d431">object::BasicSymbolRef::Flags</a>)&gt; AsmSymbol)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Parse inline ASM and collect the symbols that are defined or referenced in the current module.

For each found symbol, call <code><a href="#a39c72fdc2ed1ff4829689fb72d13f426">AsmSymbol</a></code> with the name of the symbol found and the associated flags.

### CollectAsmSymvers() {#a260eabd30cac206a16723c8cd6e0c5c4}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>void ModuleSymbolTable::CollectAsmSymvers (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module">Module</a> &amp; M, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/function-ref">function&#95;ref</a>&lt; void(<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a>, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a>)&gt; AsmSymver)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Parse inline ASM and collect the symvers directives that are defined in the current module.

For each found symbol, call <code>AsmSymver</code> with the name of the symbol and its alias.
